com.argox.sdk.barcodeprinter

Class BarcodePrinter<T extends IPrinterConnection,S extends IEmulation>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.argox.sdk.barcodeprinter.BarcodePrinter<T,S>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - The printer connection class
    S - The emulator class

    public class BarcodePrinter<T extends IPrinterConnection,S extends IEmulation>
extends java.lang.Object
    This class can be regarded as a subject, when adding the objects required for the printer output/input, the printer can be controlled to accomplish the desired results. This class needs to be instantiated before it can be used.
    See Also:
    IPrinterConnection, IEmulation
